Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be another hot day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you hot, dressed like that in the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that newspaper three days old?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said another middle aged couple \N was murdered, this time in Verden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said a doctor did it, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, you said you were \N going to Verden, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know someone living there or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll meet him there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:18.90,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,175)\pos(319,309)}An Old Soldier and a Little Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:55.86,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,130)\pos(326,371)}Giessen Police Station \N (Germany)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were originally with the French foreign legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After becoming a mercenary...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you took part in the Nicaragua war in 1979.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From 1981 to 1984...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you aided the anti-government guerrillas in Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 1987...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you played an important role in \N the Mossad's secret campaign...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to eliminate a radical Islamic faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is quite an extensive combat history...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mr. Hugo Bernhardt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the seminar was held by an excellent \N mercenary like yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I assume the graduating students were splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish our young officers would attend your class...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so they could be retrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's not necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did this man perform splendidly as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About five months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he should have come to your training ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a genius with a scalpel in his hand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was he as adept with a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to talk about my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:49.72,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,312)\fad(250,112)}5 Months Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you taught how to shoot a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were self-taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never fired a gun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I'm asking is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you are the only one I can turn to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you will have to forget everything you know \N about guns if you join my training program.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time someone who has never \N shot a gun before has come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a jump rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you have experience or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we always start with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit spacing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balance!  Keep your balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't jump as well as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always supervise the training \N for the instructor like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to stare at me like that.  I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to do it, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a brambling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she is looking for food for her chicks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too tired to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating is also part of the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your daughter...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, your granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who killed her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right in front of her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened in Myanmar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I went into a  hut in the jungle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I found those two inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mother was holding a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had hesitated, I would have been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I brought her back with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she started living with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she has never smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She will probably live the rest of her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what happens when you hold a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't hold a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like daphne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time for you to go running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that is right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you are done with that, come to \N the depression behind the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The depression?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The firing range...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When shooting a gun, always pull the trigger twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You chance of killing someone will \N rise dramatically by shooting twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't expect to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always make the food around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I made some Japanese dishes today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is called Beef Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you will like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made them by sharpening wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would feel more Japanese if we used them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are good at using chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a baby brambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have fallen down from its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!  You have to return it to its nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is very hard to raise it away from its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They rarely ever survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's return it to its nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To its mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be decided in three seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mess up or hesitate for even a split second, \N the one who will be shot and killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what grade did he graduate with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got a perfect score on his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also built a fundamental level of stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overall his concentration was absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he had to kill a person with a \N gun, it would be another story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he can kill his first person or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that is where the path splits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Between whether he can use a gun or not, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think he will take?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that does not matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you know where he is headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I would very much like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the past five months.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the payment for the rest of the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, please eat Beef Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know where he is headed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
